headline: WorkJam Raises the Bar for Frontline Operations Platforms with Major Release
summary: WorkJam, the leading frontline operations platform, today announced a major release that enables retailers to verify execution, surface the right data to the right people, and put AI to work where it matters: inside workflows, not beside them.
